<br>
What was the difference?<br>
2 days ago I had at the start a room only filled with &quot;normal&quot; Needlites. I could kill them without big problems. So the next times I never had a full room but the MOBs respawned as I killed them before. So when I got the Queen, she was always alone and I could kill her 3 times.<br>
