First I killed one solo-Needlite but the Queen was surrounded by 2 other Needlites. I thought 1 maybe wouldnt help her.<br>
I did send my Pet to the Queen. (was a 26-dmg-Pet, so the 2nd best I could get). It went down pretty fast, I healed..got 1 of the MObs on me, I could still get one more heal off, but the Pet died quickly nevertheless and a few seconds later I was dead.<br>
<br>
Ok, I still *wanted* to have another successful day, so I went in again.<br>
This time I made sure that I have a 28-dmg-Fire-Pet, so the best I could get. I also DS'ed myself this time.<br>
